Tidio is a live chat and chatbot platform designed to enhance customer communication on websites. It integrates live chat, AI-powered chatbots, and email features into a single platform, allowing businesses to provide real-time customer support and automate responses. Tidio can be used to engage visitors, resolve issues quickly, and improve customer experience, often leading to higher conversions. It also integrates with various e-commerce platforms like Shopify, WordPress, and others, making it a versatile tool for businesses looking to streamline customer interactions.
